# RASCAL - Control Architecture

## 🎯 System Overview

RASCAL is an autonomous delivery robot with dual control modes:
1. **Manual Mode** - Direct control via Bluetooth mobile app
2. **Autonomous Mode** - GPS waypoint navigation with obstacle awareness

