## 🔄 Control Flow

### State Machine

```
┌─────────────┐
│   STOPPED   │◄─────────────────┐
└──────┬──────┘                  │
       │                         │
       │ FWD/BWD/LEFT/RIGHT      │ STOP command
       ▼                         │
┌─────────────┐                  │
│   MANUAL    │──────────────────┤
│    MODE     │                  │
└──────┬──────┘                  │
       │                         │
       │ GOTO:LAT,LON            │
       ▼                         │
┌─────────────┐                  │
│ AUTONOMOUS  │                  │
│    MODE     │──────────────────┤
└─────────────┘                  │
       │                         │
       │ Waypoint reached        │
       └─────────────────────────┘
```

### Manual Mode Flow

```
Bluetooth Command Received
        │
        ▼
  Parse Command
        │
        ├─► "FWD"   ──► moveForward(BASE_SPEED)
        ├─► "BWD"   ──► moveBackward(BASE_SPEED)
        ├─► "LEFT"  ──► turnLeft(TURN_SPEED)
        ├─► "RIGHT" ──► turnRight(TURN_SPEED)
        └─► "STOP"  ──► stopMotors()
```

### Autonomous Navigation Flow

```
GOTO:LAT,LON Command
        │
        ▼
Set Target Waypoint
        │
        ▼
┌───────────────────┐
│  Navigation Loop  │
└────────┬──────────┘
         │
         ▼
  Read GPS Position
         │
         ▼
  Calculate Distance
  to Waypoint
         │
         ├─► < 3m? ──► STOP (Waypoint Reached)
         │
         └─► > 3m
              │
              ▼
         Calculate Bearing
         to Waypoint
              │
              ▼
         Calculate Heading
         Error
              │
              ├─► Error < 15° ──► moveForward()
              ├─► Error > 15° ──► turnRight()
              └─► Error < -15° ─► turnLeft()
              │
              └─► Loop back
```

