## ⚡ Motor Control

### 4-Wheel Drive Configuration

```
      Front
   FL      FR
    ●------●
    |  ▲   |
    |  |   |  Forward direction
    |      |
    ●------●
   BL      BR
```

### Movement Primitives

| Movement | FL | FR | BL | BR |
|----------|----|----|----|----||
| Forward  | ↑  | ↑  | ↑  | ↑  |
| Backward | ↓  | ↓  | ↓  | ↓  |
| Turn Left (Tank) | ↓  | ↑  | ↓  | ↑  |
| Turn Right (Tank) | ↑  | ↓  | ↑  | ↓  |
| Stop | ●  | ●  | ●  | ●  |

### PWM Speed Control

- **Base Speed:** 200/255 (78% power) - Good for straight movement
- **Turn Speed:** 180/255 (71% power) - Slower for precise turns
- **Range:** 0-255 (8-bit PWM)

