## 🚀 Upgrade Path to Prototype 2 (ROS + Lidar)

### Architecture Comparison

| Feature | Prototype 1 (Current) | Prototype 2 (ROS) |
|---------|----------------------|--------------------|
| Brain | Arduino Mega | Raspberry Pi 4 |
| Navigation | GPS waypoints | GPS + SLAM |
| Obstacle Detection | None | RPLidar A1 |
| Localization | GPS only | GPS + IMU + Odometry |
| Mapping | None | Real-time 2D map |
| Framework | Arduino C++ | ROS Noetic/Melodic |
| Control | Direct motor control | ROS Navigation Stack |

### ROS Node Architecture (Future)

```
/gps_node → publishes GPS data
    ↓
/localization_node → fuses GPS + IMU + odometry
    ↓
/navigation_node → path planning (A*, DWA)
    ↓
/motor_control_node → Arduino bridge
    ↓
Arduino (motor driver)
```

