## 📐 Performance Specifications

### Speed
- **Maximum Speed:** ~0.5 m/s (1.8 km/h) at BASE_SPEED=200
- **Turn Rate:** ~45°/second
- **Acceleration:** Instant (no ramping in current design)

### Navigation
- **Waypoint Accuracy:** ±3 meters
- **Path Type:** Direct line-of-sight (no obstacle avoidance)
- **Update Cycle:** 1 Hz (limited by GPS)

### Communication
- **Bluetooth Range:** ~10 meters (line of sight)
- **Latency:** <100ms command response
- **Baud Rate:** 9600 bps (sufficient for commands)

