## 🐛 Error Handling

### GPS Loss
```
if (!gps.location.isValid()) {
    stopMotors();
    // Wait for fix recovery
}
```

### Bluetooth Disconnection
- Robot continues last command (manual mode)
- Completes waypoint navigation (autonomous mode)
- Status LED blinks rapidly

### Low Battery (Future Enhancement)
- Add voltage divider to monitor battery
- Return to home waypoint at <20% capacity

